events.name: telos.haus community social (April)
events.description:
Join us for a (free) community social hour at telos.haus! Take a break from work with drinks, meet new people, and mingle with other creatives. This is the perfect opportunity to get a sense of our space and connect with others by breaking bread.

Light snacks provided. Bring your own lunch or something to share if you're feeling generous!
